node.text: We're excited to welcome our third trusted NGO miner Project child to the ETN family! node.text:
The blockchain update will enable the ETN-Network to much more easily integrate with smart contracts, DeFi, and even wallet synchronisation.
Read all about it: https://bit.ly/3Ev5sDI
.
.
.
#blockchainupdate #companyupdate #future #ETN_Network #ETN #Electroneum #cryptocurrency #crypto #blockchain #blockchaintechnology #worldwide #global #globalmarket #digital #online #business

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Electroneum on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'ETN-Network'.

node.text:
The direction of travel for the entire blockchain industry is away from privacy coins, with some countries banning them outright. As such we've made some changes to the Electroneum blockchain. Check out Richard Ells' new update video: https://bit.ly/3DK1Ugk
.
.
.
#ETN_Network #ETN #Electroneum #cryptocurrency #crypto #blockchain #blockchaintechnology #worldwide #global #blockchainupdate #update #companyupdate

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Electroneum on September 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'ETN-Network'.

node.text:
Smart contracts are the the first step on the ETN-Network roadmap. Find out about how the new blockchain update can achieve this in the ETN-Network update! This will take place at block height 1,175,315.
https://bit.ly/3Ev5sDI
.
.
.
#ETN_Network #ETN #Electroneum #cryptocurrency #crypto #blockchain #entrepreneur #blockchaintechnology #worldwide #global #globalmarket #digital #online #business

With the likes of Bittrex and Shapeshift delisting privacy coins, and various countries outright banning privacy coins, The ETN-Network blockchain will be going completely public on the 30th September. https://bit.ly/3DK1Ugk

#blockchain #update #public #global #crypto

https://bit.ly/3DK1Ugk
